---
title: Teriyaki Prawn Noodles with pak choi and refeshing salad
description: This vibrant dish takes inspiration from East Asian flavours. Prawns are pan-seared to a tender finish and glazed in a rich teriyaki sauce. Added crunch is provided by the spicy and fresh cucumber salad.
